    "body": "This formatting would go against the [Solidity style guide](https://docs.soliditylang.org/en/latest/style-guide.html#whitespace-in-expressions) though —\r\n\r\n> ## Whitespace in Expressions\r\n> Avoid extraneous whitespace in the following situations:\r\n>   …\r\n> More than one space around an assignment or other operator to align with another:\r\n> \r\n> **Yes:**\r\n> ```\r\n> x = 1;\r\n> y = 2;\r\n> longVariable = 3;\r\n> ```\r\n> \r\n> **No:**\r\n> \r\n> ```\r\n> x            = 1;\r\n> y            = 2;\r\n> longVariable = 3;\r\n> ```",
